Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:12.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Headed for the forbidden land, Chor\NTempest makes a startling discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:17.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins.
